"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-why-runners-wear-arm-sleeves-paris-olympics-b1174820.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Over the weekend, the track and field events began at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the most popular events of the Games, theathleticsactionhas included a dramatic men's 100m final whenNoah Lyles came from behind to pip Kishane Thompsonby five thousandths of a second and take gold for USA.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998809762545, \"rank\": 6.626295973443076e-08, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's 100m final was equally as exciting.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Julien Alfred, the 23-year-old St Lucian,powered away from Sha'Carri Richardson to claim gold- and win the first ever Olympic medal for the Caribbean nation.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\", \"score\": 0.9798768061948612, \"rank\": 0.02053636760892891, \"text\": \"Lucian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucian\"}, {\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers of the weekend's events might have spotted that some of the athletes competing inrunningwere wearing arm sleeves.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While they undoubtedly add a splash of style to any running outfit, arm sleeves offer much more than just aesthetic appeal.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These accessories have gained popularity among athletes for a range of practical benefits, from performance enhancement to recovery support.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the main reasons some runners opt for arm sleeves is to protect their skin from the sun's harmful ultraviolet (UV) rays.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While sunscreen can be effective, it often needs reapplication during longer distance runs, and can be uncomfortable when mixed with sweat.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Arm sleeves made with UV-resistant materials provide consistent protection without the need for reapplication, allowing runners to focus on their performance rather than worrying about sunburn or long-term skin damage.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Olympians, compression technology is probably the main reason for the popularity of arm sleeves.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The snug fit of compression sleeves applies gentle pressure to the muscles in the arms, which can enhance circulation and increase oxygen delivery to the muscles.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This improved blood flow can lead to better performance and reduced muscle fatigue.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Compression can also aid in recovery by decreasing the buildup of lactic acid and minimising muscle soreness after a run.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Arm sleeves can also play an important role in temperature regulation, making them suitable for both hot and cold conditions.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In cooler weather, the sleeves act as an additional layer that helps retain body heat, keeping muscles warm and reducing the risk of injury.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBA London 2026 LIVE: Memphis Grizzlies vs Orlando Magic come to the UK  Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Winter escapes and activities to end the year in style  Conversely, in warmer climates, specially designed sleeves made from moisture-wicking fabrics can help keep runners cool by drawing sweat away from the skin and allowing it to evaporate more efficiently.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999714277696, \"rank\": 2.8274390091498422e-08, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999714268601, \"rank\": 2.7859690628169206e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.725511501393154e-15, \"text\": \"Memphis Grizzlies\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Memphis_Grizzlies\"}, {\"begin\": 2469, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7490262369472813, \"rank\": 0.3350667157340616, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicte